# Testing & Quality

## Quality Gates

### Before Transport Checklist

- [ ] Code Inspector (SCI): 0 errors, 0 warnings
- [ ] Extended Check (SLIN): 0 errors, 0 warnings
- [ ] All breakpoints removed
- [ ] All dead code removed
- [ ] No 7.40+ syntax
- [ ] Authorization checks present
- [ ] Exception handling implemented
- [ ] Documentation complete
- [ ] SY-SUBRC checks after operations
- [ ] Text elements used (no hard-coded text)

## Performance Verification

- [ ] SAT/SE30: Runtime analysis
- [ ] ST05: SQL trace (no full table scans)
- [ ] Database time < 50% of total
- [ ] Response time < 3 seconds (online)

## ABAP Unit

```abap
CLASS ltc_test DEFINITION FOR TESTING
  RISK LEVEL HARMLESS
  DURATION SHORT.

  PRIVATE SECTION.
    DATA: mo_cut TYPE REF TO zcl_material_processor.
    
    METHODS: setup,
             test_process_material FOR TESTING.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS ltc_test IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD setup.
    CREATE OBJECT mo_cut
      EXPORTING
        iv_plant = '1000'.
  ENDMETHOD.

  METHOD test_process_material.
    DATA: lv_result TYPE abap_bool.
    
    lv_result = mo_cut->process_material( iv_matnr = 'TEST123' ).
    
    cl_abap_unit_assert=>assert_equals(
      act = lv_result
      exp = abap_true ).
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.
